       ENVIRONMENT DIVISION.
       CONFIGURATION SECTION.
       SPECIAL-NAMES.
           DECIMAL-POINT IS COMMA.
       INPUT-OUTPUT SECTION.
       FILE-CONTROL.
           SELECT PSFICHPS2 ASSIGN         TO DISK-PSFICHPS2
                              FILE STATUS  IS WS-PSFICHPS2-STATUS.
       DATA DIVISION.
       FILE SECTION.
       FD  PSFICHPS2.
       01  PSFICHPS2-RECORD              PIC X(340).
