           EXEC SQL INCLUDE PSCDFICHRL END-EXEC.
           EXEC SQL INCLUDE PSCDFICH5  END-EXEC.
      * TABELA PSPARAM   (PARAMETRIZAÇĂO)
           EXEC SQL INCLUDE PSCDPARAM  END-EXEC.
