              MOVE '1000-INICIO-PROGRAMA.' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              MOVE 'VIAL0001-CALLERID'     TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-NM(1)
              MOVE VIAL0001-CALLERID       TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR(1)
