              THRU AQCP0101-OBT-DADOS-ARQ-EXIT

           MOVE VIAL0001-MENSAGEM-INPUT    TO PSCV4010-MSG.
           MOVE PSCV4010-ASE               TO PSCV4011-ASE.
           MOVE SPACES                     TO PSCV4011-PILMSG.
           MOVE ZEROES                     TO WS-HEADER-NOCB
           INITIALIZE                         PSCL5230-DATA.
