              MOVE  PSCV4010-PIREFORD-B-ST TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR(3)(5:)
              MOVE  PSCV4010-PITREG-B-ST   TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR(3)(9:)
              MOVE  PSCV4010-PINCLI-C-ST   TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR(3)(13:)
              MOVE  PSCV4010-PIDINT-C-ST   TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR(3)(29:)
              MOVE  PSCV4010-PIFORM-B-ST   TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR(3)(33:)
              MOVE  PSCV4010-PIREFORD-B-ST TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR(3)(37:)
              MOVE  PSCV4010-PITREG-B-ST   TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR(3)(41:)
              MOVE PSCV4010-PIIPAGSAL-C-ST TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR(3)(45:)
              MOVE 'VIAL0001-CALLERID'     TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-NM(4)
              MOVE VIAL0001-CALLERID       TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR(4)
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.
