ESTST *    PERFORM 1100-VALIDA-FORMATO
ESTST *       THRU 1100-VALIDA-FORMATO-EXIT.
      *
      **R 2015
           PERFORM ETCP0002-FORM-ONLINE-IN
              THRU ETCP0002-FORM-ONLINE-IN-EXIT
      **R 2015

           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
              PERFORM 1105-VALIDA-DATA-INT
                 THRU 1105-VALIDA-DATA-INT-EXIT
