              PERFORM 1120-VALIDA-CONTA
                 THRU 1120-VALIDA-CONTA-EXIT
           END-IF.
ES0731*
ES0731     IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
ES0731     AND PSCV4010-PIIENVF EQUAL CON-SIM
ES0731        PERFORM 2200-VALIDA-TIPO-PAG
ES0731           THRU 2200-VALIDA-TIPO-PAG-EXIT
ES0731     END-IF.
ES0731*
       1099-INICIO-PROGRAMA-EXIT.
           EXIT.

      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            1105-VALIDA-DATA-INT
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       1105-VALIDA-DATA-INT.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '1105-VALIDA-DATA-INT'  TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              MOVE 'PSCV4010-PIFORM    '   TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-NM(1)
              MOVE PSCV4010-PIFORM         TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR(1)
              MOVE 'PSCV4010-PIDINT    '   TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-NM(2)
              MOVE PSCV4010-PIDINT         TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR(2)
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.
      *
           IF PSCV4010-PIDINT LESS THAN '2005-01-01'
              MOVE PSCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO   TO PSCV4011-PIDINT-S
      **R     MOVE PSCK0001-O-DATA-INV      TO PSCV4011-PIDINT-MSG
              MOVE PSCK0001-ERR-HRDINT      TO PSCV4011-PIDINT-MSG
              MOVE PSCK0002-CAPLIC-PS       TO PSCV4011-PIDINT-CAPLIC
              SET VIAL0002-ERROS-FUNCAO     TO TRUE
           END-IF.
      *
       1105-VALIDA-DATA-INT-EXIT.
           EXIT.

      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            1100-VALIDA-FORMATO
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       1100-VALIDA-FORMATO.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '1100-VALIDA-FORMATO'   TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              MOVE 'PSCV4010-PIFORM    '   TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-NM(1)
              MOVE PSCV4010-PIFORM         TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR(1)
              MOVE 'PSCV4010-PIDINT    '   TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-NM(2)
              MOVE PSCV4010-PIDINT         TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR(2)
