           MOVE PSCK0002-TAB-FORMATOS      TO ARCL5005-CTABELA.
           MOVE PSCV4010-PIFORM            TO ARCL5005-CCOD.
           MOVE SPACES                     TO ARCL5005-C2COD.
           MOVE PSCK0002-PT-PT             TO ARCL5005-CLINGUA.
      *
           PERFORM CALL-ARM5005
              THRU CALL-ARM5005-EXIT.
      *
           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '1100-VALIDA-FORMATO'   TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              MOVE 'ETCL0002-IND-ERROS '   TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-NM(1)
              MOVE ETCL0002-IND-ERROS      TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR(1)
              MOVE 'ARCL5005-GDESC     '   TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-NM(2)
              MOVE ARCL5005-GDESC          TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR(2)
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.
      *
           IF NOT ETCL0002-SEM-ERROS
              SET  PSCV4011-PIFORM-1       TO TRUE
              MOVE PSCK0002-CAPLIC-PS      TO PSCV4011-PIFORM-CAPLIC
              MOVE PSCK0001-FORMATO-INVALIDO
                                           TO PSCV4011-PIFORM-MSG
              MOVE SXCL0002-IND-ERROS      TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
