           MOVE SPACES                      TO PSFICHEIR-FCUSRCNF
           MOVE PSCK0002-SEM-BYPASS         TO PSFICHEIR-FCINDBYP.
           MOVE VIAL0001-ORIGEM             TO PSFICHEIR-FCCANAL.
           MOVE PSCV4010-PINCLI-B           TO PSFICHEIR-FCNCLIB.
      *    MOVE PSCV4010-PINATRA-B          TO PSFICHEIR-FCNATRB.
      *    MOVE PSCV4010-PINSEQA-B          TO PSFICHEIR-FCNSEQB.
           MOVE PSCV4010-PICONTA-B          TO PSFICHEIR-FCCONTAB.
