           MOVE PSCV4010-PIREFORD-B         TO PSFICHEIR-FCREFORDB.
           MOVE PSCV4010-PIMONT-B           TO PSFICHEIR-FCMONTB.
           MOVE PSCV4010-PITREG-B           TO PSFICHEIR-FCTREGB.
           MOVE PSCV4010-PINCLI-C           TO PSFICHEIR-FCNCLIC.
      *    MOVE PSCV4010-PINATRA-C          TO PSFICHEIR-FCNATRC.
      *    MOVE PSCV4010-PINSEQA-C          TO PSFICHEIR-FCNSEQC.
