                TO PSCV4011-PINCLI-S
              MOVE PSCK0001-PINCLI-N-EXISTS
                TO PSCV4011-PINCLI-MSG
              MOVE PSCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO
                TO PSCV4011-PIDINT-S
              MOVE PSCK0001-PIDINT-N-EXISTS
                TO PSCV4011-PIDINT-MSG
           ELSE
              PERFORM 4000-COBRA-COMISSAO
                 THRU 4000-COBRA-COMISSAO-EXIT
