              MOVE 'STATUS'                TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-NM(2)
              MOVE WS-PSFICHPS2-STATUS     TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR(2)
              MOVE 'Data online '          TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-NM(3)
              MOVE VIAL0001-DATA-EXTRN     TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR(3)
