                 INITIALIZE RPARAM
                 MOVE PSCK0002-PARAM-DAT   TO PSPARAM-PRPARAM
                 PERFORM 2300-PARAM-MSG-ERRO
                    THRU 2399-PARAM-MSG-ERRO-EXIT

                 STRING PSCV4011-PILMSG DELIMITED BY '  '
                        PSPARAM-PRPARM0 DELIMITED BY '  '
                  '. ' DELIMITED BY '  ' INTO PSCV4011-PILMSG

              END-IF
      **R 2026-02-11
              MOVE CON-SIM                 TO PSCV4011-PIICONT
              MOVE CON-SIM                 TO PSCV4011-PIICANC
              MOVE PSCV4010-PINCLI         TO PSCV4011-PINCLI-B
      **R

              PERFORM 4000-OBTEM-CONTA
                 THRU 4000-OBTEM-CONTA-EXIT

      **R 20150421
      **R     MOVE PSCWPS2-ORD-NCLI        TO PSCV4011-PINCLI-B
      **R     MOVE PSCWPS2-ORD-NATR        TO PSCV4011-PINATRA-B
      **R     MOVE PSCWPS2-ORD-NSEQ        TO PSCV4011-PICONTA-B
