      **R     MOVE AQCW0008-NCLI11         TO AQCW0008-NCLI23
      **R     MOVE AQCW0008-NATR11         TO AQCW0008-NATR23
      **R     MOVE AQCW0008-NSEQ11         TO AQCW0008-NSEQ23
      **R     MOVE AQCW0008-CONTA23        TO PSCV4011-PICONTA-B

      * CONVERTE DATA DE 9(08) PARA X(10)
              MOVE PSCWPS2-DATA-PROCESSO   TO AQCW0005-DT98
              PERFORM AQCP0005-CONV-DT8INDT10
                 THRU AQCP0005-CONV-DT8INDT10-EXIT
              MOVE AQCW0005-DTX10          TO PSCV4011-PIDINT-B
              MOVE PSCV4010-PIFORM         TO PSCV4011-PIFORM-B
              MOVE PSCWPS2-ORD-REFERENCIA  TO PSCV4011-PIREFORD-B
           ELSE
              IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
                 MOVE 'NOT HEADER '        TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
                 MOVE 'REGISTO 9=TRAILER ' TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-NM(1)
                 MOVE PSCWPS2-TIPO-REGISTO TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR(1)
      **R        MOVE 'VALOR: '            TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-NM(2)
      **R        MOVE PSCWPS2-VALOR        TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR(2)
                 MOVE 'TOTAL: '            TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-NM(3)
                 MOVE PSCWPS2-TOTAL-VALORES TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR(3)
                 MOVE 'REGISTOS: '         TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-NM(4)
                 MOVE PSCWPS2-TOTAL-REGISTOS TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR(4)
                 PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                    THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
              END-IF

              IF PSCWPS2-REG-TRAILER
                 MOVE 0                    TO WS-MONT
                 MOVE 0                    TO WS-NREG
                 MOVE PSCWPS2-TOTAL-VALORES
                                           TO WS-MONT
                 MOVE PSCWPS2-TOTAL-REGISTOS
                                           TO WS-NREG
                 MOVE WS-MONT              TO PSCV4011-PIMONT-B
                 MOVE WS-NREG              TO PSCV4011-PITREG-B
              ELSE
                 ADD PSCWPS2-VALOR         TO WS-MONT
                 ADD CON-1                 TO WS-NREG
              END-IF
           END-IF.

           READ PSFICHPS2.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2180  APOS READ   '    TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              MOVE 'RECORD'                TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-NM(2)
              MOVE PSFICHPS2-RECORD        TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR(2)
              MOVE 'STATUS'                TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-NM(1)
