              MOVE PSFICHPS2-RECORD        TO WS-RECORD-ALL
           ELSE
              IF NOT WS-PSFICHPS2-EOF
              SET VIAL0002-ERROS-FUNCAO    TO TRUE
           END-IF.

           IF NOT VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
              MOVE PSCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO
                TO PSCV4011-PINCLI-S
              MOVE PSCK0001-PINCLI-N-EXISTS
                TO PSCV4011-PINCLI-MSG
              MOVE PSCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO
                TO PSCV4011-PICONTA-S
              MOVE PSCK0001-PINSEQA-N-EXISTS
                TO PSCV4011-PICONTA-MSG
              MOVE PSCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO
                TO PSCV4011-PIDINT-S
              MOVE PSCK0001-PIDINT-N-EXISTS
                TO PSCV4011-PIDINT-MSG
              MOVE PSCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO
                TO PSCV4011-PIFORM-S
              MOVE PSCK0001-PIFORM-N-EXISTS
                TO PSCV4011-PIFORM-MSG
              MOVE PSCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO
                TO PSCV4011-PIREFORD-S
              MOVE PSCK0001-PIREFORD-N-EXISTS
                TO PSCV4011-PIREFORD-MSG
              MOVE PSCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO
                TO PSCV4011-PITPROC-S
              MOVE PSCK0001-PITPROC-N-EXISTS
                TO PSCV4011-PITPROC-MSG
           END-IF.

       2189-PROCESSA-PS2-EXIT.
           EXIT.

AR0731*--------------------------------------------------------------
AR0731*                   2210-VAL-TIPO-PAGAMENTO
AR0731*--------------------------------------------------------------
AR0731 2210-VAL-TIPO-PAGAMENTO.
      *
           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2210-VAL-TIPO-PAGAMENTO' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.
      *
           MOVE PSFICHPS2-RECORD           TO PSCWPS2.
           MOVE PSCWPS2-TIPO-OPERACAO      TO WS-TIPO-OPERACAO-FICH.
           MOVE PSCV4010-PIIPAGSAL         TO WS-TIPO-OPERACAO-ECRA.
      *
           IF NOT WS-TIPO-OPERACAO-FICH-SAL
              AND WS-TIPO-OPERACAO-ECRA-SAL
      *
              MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO  TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
              MOVE PSCK0001-TIP-PAG-INV   TO PSCV4011-PIIPAGSAL-C-MSG
              MOVE PSCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO TO PSCV4011-PIIPAGSAL-C-S
              MOVE PSCK0002-CAPLIC-PS     TO PSCV4011-PIIPAGSAL-C-CAPLIC
      *
              IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
                 MOVE 'FICHEIRO NAO SALARIO E ECRA SALARIO '
                                           TO VIAL0015-CAMPOS-CHAVE
                 PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                    THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
              END-IF
           END-IF.
      *
           IF NOT WS-TIPO-OPERACAO-ECRA-SAL
              AND WS-TIPO-OPERACAO-FICH-SAL
      *
              MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO  TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
              MOVE PSCK0001-TIP-PAG-INV   TO PSCV4011-PIIPAGSAL-C-MSG
              MOVE PSCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO TO PSCV4011-PIIPAGSAL-C-S
              MOVE PSCK0002-CAPLIC-PS     TO PSCV4011-PIIPAGSAL-C-CAPLIC
      *
              IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
                 MOVE 'FICHEIRO SALARIO E ECRA NAO SALARIO '
                                           TO VIAL0015-CAMPOS-CHAVE
                 PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                    THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
              END-IF
           END-IF.
      *
           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2210-VAL-TIPO-PAGAMENTO' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              MOVE 'PSCWPS2-TIPO-OPERACAO  ' TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-NM (1)
              MOVE  PSCWPS2-TIPO-OPERACAO    TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR(1)
              MOVE 'PSCV4010-PIIPAGSAL     ' TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-NM (2)
              MOVE  PSCV4010-PIIPAGSAL       TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR(2)
              MOVE 'VIAL0002-IND-ERROS     ' TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-NM (3)
              MOVE  VIAL0002-IND-ERROS       TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR(3)
              MOVE 'PSCV4011-PIIPAGSAL-C-MSG' TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-NM(4)
              MOVE  PSCV4011-PIIPAGSAL-C-MSG TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR(4)
              MOVE 'WS-TIPO-OPERACAO-ECRA  ' TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-NM (5)
              MOVE  WS-TIPO-OPERACAO-ECRA    TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR(5)
              MOVE 'WS-TIPO-OPERACAO-FICH  ' TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-NM (6)
              MOVE  WS-TIPO-OPERACAO-FICH    TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR(6)
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.
      *
AR0731 2210-VAL-TIPO-PAGAMENTO-EXIT.
AR0731     EXIT.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            2300-PARAM-MSG-ERRO
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2300-PARAM-MSG-ERRO.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2300-PARAM-MSG-ERRO'   TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           MOVE PSCK0002-CODPAR-MSGU       TO PSPARAM-PRCODPAR.

           EXEC SQL
                SELECT  PRTIPPAR
                     ,  PRVALDAT
                     ,  PRVALNUM
                     ,  PRVALBOL
                     ,  PRPARM0
                     ,  PRPARM1
                     ,  PRPARM2
                     ,  PRPARM3
                     ,  PRPARM4
                     ,  PRPARM5
                     ,  PRPARM6
                     ,  PRPARM7
                     ,  PRPARM8
                     ,  PRPARM9
                  INTO :PSPARAM-PRTIPPAR
                     , :PSPARAM-PRVALDAT
                     , :PSPARAM-PRVALNUM
                     , :PSPARAM-PRVALBOL
                     , :PSPARAM-PRPARM0
                     , :PSPARAM-PRPARM1
                     , :PSPARAM-PRPARM2
                     , :PSPARAM-PRPARM3
                     , :PSPARAM-PRPARM4
                     , :PSPARAM-PRPARM5
                     , :PSPARAM-PRPARM6
                     , :PSPARAM-PRPARM7
                     , :PSPARAM-PRPARM8
                     , :PSPARAM-PRPARM9
                  FROM  PSPARAM
                 WHERE  PRCODPAR = :PSPARAM-PRCODPAR
                   AND  PRPARAM  = :PSPARAM-PRPARAM
           END-EXEC.

           MOVE CON-PSPARAM                TO VIAL0002-TABLE-NAME.

           PERFORM 9020-DB2CHECK
              THRU 9029-DB2CHECK-EXIT.

           IF NOT DB2-OK AND NOT DB2-NOTFND
              MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO   TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
              MOVE PSCK0001-ERR-PRPARAM    TO PSCV4011-PIDINT-C-MSG
              MOVE PSCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO  TO PSCV4011-PIDINT-C-S
           END-IF.

       2399-PARAM-MSG-ERRO-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            2900-FORMATA-OUTPUT
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2900-FORMATA-OUTPUT.
      *
           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2900-FORMATA-OUTPUT'   TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID

              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           MOVE PSCV4010-PINCLI            TO PSCV4011-PINCLI.
           MOVE WS-NOME-CLI                TO PSCV4011-PINMCLI.
      *
           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE 'APOS MOVE N CLI    '   TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID

              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

      * DADOS DE ECRA
           MOVE 0                          TO PSCV4011-PINCLI
      *                                       PSCV4011-PICONTA
                                              PSCV4011-PIMONT
                                              PSCV4011-PITREG    .
           MOVE PSCV4010-PINCLI            TO PSCV4011-PINCLI    .
      *    MOVE PSCV4010-PINATRA           TO PSCV4011-PINATRA   .
      *    MOVE PSCV4010-PINSEQA           TO PSCV4011-PICONTA   .
           MOVE PSCV4010-PICONTA          TO PSCV4011-PICONTA  .
           MOVE PSCV4010-PIDINT            TO PSCV4011-PIDINT    .
           MOVE PSCV4010-PIFORM            TO PSCV4011-PIFORM    .
           MOVE PSCV4010-PIREFORD          TO PSCV4011-PIREFORD  .
           MOVE PSCV4010-PIMONT            TO PSCV4011-PIMONT    .
           MOVE PSCV4010-PITREG            TO PSCV4011-PITREG    .
           MOVE PSCV4010-PITPROC           TO PSCV4011-PITPROC   .
           MOVE PSCV4010-PINOMEO           TO PSCV4011-PINOMEO   .
           MOVE PSCV4010-PINOMEF           TO PSCV4011-PINOMEF   .
           MOVE PSCV4010-PIIENVF           TO PSCV4011-PIIENVF   .
           MOVE PSCV4010-PICHKSO           TO PSCV4011-PICHKSO   .
           MOVE PSCV4010-PICHKSC           TO PSCV4011-PICHKSC   .
           MOVE PSCV4010-PIBIBLI           TO PSCV4011-PIBIBLI   .

      * DADOS EDITAVEIS (DEFAULT DO FICHEIRO - FICHEIRO INVALIDO VAZIO
           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '**2900-FORMATA 4'   TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              MOVE 'PSCL5230-INDINV '      TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-NM(1)
              MOVE  PSCL5230-INDINV        TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR(1)
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF

           IF PSCL5230-INDINV EQUAL CON-NAO
              MOVE PSCV4011-PINCLI-B       TO PSCV4011-PINCLI-C
      *       MOVE PSCV4011-PINATRA-B      TO PSCV4011-PINATRA-C
      *       MOVE PSCV4011-PICONTA-B      TO PSCV4011-PICONTA-C
              MOVE PSCV4011-PICONTA-B      TO PSCV4011-PICONTA-C
              MOVE PSCV4011-PIDINT-B       TO PSCV4011-PIDINT-C
              MOVE PSCV4011-PIFORM-B       TO PSCV4011-PIFORM-C
ES            IF PSCV4011-PIREFORD EQUAL SPACES
ES               MOVE PSCV4011-PIREFORD-B  TO PSCV4011-PIREFORD-C
ES            ELSE
ES               MOVE PSCV4011-PIREFORD    TO PSCV4011-PIREFORD-C
ES            END-IF
              MOVE PSCV4011-PIMONT-B       TO PSCV4011-PIMONT-C
              MOVE PSCV4011-PITREG-B       TO PSCV4011-PITREG-C
           ELSE
              MOVE 0                       TO PSCV4011-PINCLI-B
                                              PSCV4011-PICONTA-B
              MOVE SPACES                  TO PSCV4011-PIDINT-B
                                              PSCV4011-PIFORM-B
                                              PSCV4011-PIREFORD-B
              MOVE 0                       TO PSCV4011-PIMONT-B
                                              PSCV4011-PITREG-B
              MOVE 0                       TO PSCV4011-PINCLI-C
                                              PSCV4011-PICONTA-C
              MOVE SPACES                  TO PSCV4011-PIDINT-C
                                              PSCV4011-PIFORM-C
                                              PSCV4011-PIREFORD-C
              MOVE 0                       TO PSCV4011-PIMONT-C
                                              PSCV4011-PITREG-C
           END-IF.
      *
           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE 'valida diferença ' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              MOVE 'cli     '          TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-NM(1)
              MOVE PSCV4010-PINCLI     TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR(1)
              MOVE ' B: '              TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR(1)(10:04)
              MOVE PSCV4011-PINCLI-B   TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR(1)(15:9)
              MOVE 'nat     '          TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-NM(2)
              MOVE 'dint    '          TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-NM(4)
              MOVE PSCV4010-PIDINT     TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR(4)
              MOVE ' B: '              TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR(4)(11:04)
              MOVE PSCV4011-PIDINT-B   TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR(4)(15:10)
              MOVE 'mont    '          TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-NM(5)
              MOVE PSCV4010-PIMONT     TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR(5)
              MOVE ' B: '              TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR(5)(15:04)
              MOVE PSCV4011-PIMONT-B   TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR(5)(20:15)
              MOVE 'registos'          TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-NM(6)
              MOVE PSCV4010-PITREG     TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR(6)
              MOVE ' B: '              TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR(6)(17:04)
              MOVE PSCV4011-PITREG-B   TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR(6)(21:17)
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

      *    MENSAGEM DE OUTPUT COM ERROS
           IF PSCV4010-PINCLI  NOT EQUAL  PSCV4011-PINCLI-B OR
              PSCV4010-PICONTA NOT EQUAL  PSCV4011-PICONTA-B OR
              PSCV4010-PIDINT  NOT EQUAL  PSCV4011-PIDINT-B  OR
              PSCV4010-PIMONT  NOT EQUAL  PSCV4011-PIMONT-B  OR
              PSCV4010-PITREG  NOT EQUAL  PSCV4011-PITREG-B

              INITIALIZE RPARAM
              MOVE PSCK0002-PARAM-DIF      TO PSPARAM-PRPARAM

              PERFORM 2300-PARAM-MSG-ERRO
                 THRU 2399-PARAM-MSG-ERRO-EXIT

              STRING PSCV4011-PILMSG DELIMITED BY '  '
                     PSPARAM-PRPARM0 DELIMITED BY '  '
                  '. ' DELIMITED BY '  ' INTO PSCV4011-PILMSG
           END-IF.

       2999-FORMATA-OUTPUT-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            3000-FINAL-PROGRAMA
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       3000-FINAL-PROGRAMA.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '3000-FINAL-PROGRAMA.' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              MOVE 'MENSAGEM '             TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-NM(1)
              MOVE PSCV4011-PILMSG(01:40)  TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR(1)
              MOVE PSCV4011-PILMSG(41:40)  TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-NM(2)
              MOVE PSCV4011-PILMSG(81:20)  TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR(2)
              MOVE 'VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS  '  TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-NM(3)
              MOVE  VIAL0002-IND-ERROS     TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR(3)
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           MOVE PSCV4011-MSG               TO VIAL0001-MENSAGEM-OUTPUT.
           MOVE PSCV4011-LENGTH            TO VIAL0001-LENGTH-MSG.
           MOVE PSCV4011-NR-CAMPOS         TO VIAL0001-NR-CAMPOS.
           MOVE ZEROES                     TO VIAL0001-OCORRENCIAS.

       3099-FINAL-PROGRAMA-EXIT.
           EXIT.

      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            4000-COBRA-COMISSAO
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       4000-COBRA-COMISSAO.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '3000-FINAL-PROGRAMA.' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
              PERFORM 5050-CONSULTA-CONTA
                 THRU 5050-CONSULTA-CONTA-EXIT
           END-IF.

           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
              PERFORM 5050-OBTEM-DADOS-CONTRATO
                 THRU 5050-OBTEM-DADOS-CONTRATO-EXIT
           END-IF.

           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
              PERFORM 5100-CALCULA-COMISSOES
                 THRU 5100-CALCULA-COMISSOES-EXIT
           END-IF.

           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
              PERFORM 5500-COBRANCA-DESPESAS
                 THRU 5500-COBRANCA-DESPESAS-EXIT
           END-IF.

       4000-COBRA-COMISSAO-EXIT.
           EXIT.

      ******************************************************************
       5050-OBTEM-DADOS-CONTRATO.
      ******************************************************************

           IF VIAL0015-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '5050-OBTEM-DADOS-CONTRATO' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           INITIALIZE PSCL5250-DATA.
           MOVE PSCV4010-PINCLI            TO PSCL5250-NCLI.
           EVALUATE PSCV4010-PIIPAGSAL
             WHEN PSCK0002-TREMUN-SALARIO
             WHEN PSCK0002-TREMUN-BONUS
               MOVE PSCK0002-TOPE-SALARIO  TO PSCL5250-TSERV
             WHEN PSCK0002-TREMUN-FORNEC
               MOVE PSCK0002-TOPE-FORNEC   TO PSCL5250-TSERV
           END-EVALUATE

           IF VIAL0015-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '5050-OBTEM-DADOS-CONTRATO' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              MOVE 'PSCL5250-TSERV           ' TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-NM(1)
              MOVE PSCL5250-TSERV              TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR(1)
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.


           MOVE ZEROES                     TO PSCL5250-NTRY
           MOVE SPACES                     TO PSCL5250-TMOV
           MOVE SPACES                     TO PSCL5250-DESC
           MOVE WS-PROGNAME                TO PSCL5250-PGMC.

           MOVE VIAL0001-CALLERID             TO PSCL5250-JOBNC.
           MOVE VIAL0001-CUSER-EXTRN       TO PSCL5250-USERC.
           MOVE VIAL0001-MSGQ              TO PSCL5250-PGMQC.
           MOVE PSCK0002-RCODE-OK          TO PSCL5250-RCODE.
           MOVE PSCK0002-ESTR-NEXE         TO PSCL5250-ESTR.
           MOVE PSCK0002-APTR-APL          TO PSCL5250-APTR.
           MOVE VIAL0001-CBANCO            TO PSCL5250-AT-CBAN
           MOVE VIAL0001-CBALM             TO PSCL5250-AT-BALM
           MOVE VIAL0001-DATA-EXTRN        TO PSCL5250-AT-DTOP
           MOVE VIAL0001-CMOEDA            TO PSCL5250-AT-CMOE
           MOVE VIAL0001-I-DEBUG           TO PSCL5250-AT-DEBUG

           CALL CON-PSM5250 USING ETCL0002-COMMAREA
                                  PSCL5250-DATA.

           MOVE PSCL5250-RCODE             TO AQCW0009-RCODE.

           IF VIAL0015-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE 'CALL PSM5250'       TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              MOVE 'PSCL5250-RCODE'     TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-NM  (1)
              MOVE  PSCL5250-RCODE      TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR (1)
              MOVE 'PSCL5250-CODERR'    TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-NM  (2)
              MOVE  PSCL5250-CODERR     TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR (2)
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           IF NOT AQCW0009-SEM-ERROS
              MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO     TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
              MOVE PSCK0001-SELECT-PSCONTRAT TO PSCV4011-PIDINT-C-MSG
              MOVE PSCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO    TO PSCV4011-PIDINT-C-S
           END-IF.

       5050-OBTEM-DADOS-CONTRATO-EXIT.
           EXIT.

      ******************************************************************
       5050-CONSULTA-CONTA.
      ******************************************************************
      *
           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '5050-CONSULTA-CONTA    ' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.
      *
           INITIALIZE SXCL0170-DATA.

      *    MOVE ETCL0050-VERSAO          TO SXCL0170-VERSAO
      *    SET SXCL0170-V203             TO TRUE.
           MOVE VIAL0001-VERSAO-SYS      TO SXCL0170-VERSAO
           MOVE CON-PRG-NAME             TO SXCL0170-PGMC  .
           MOVE PSCK0002-TTR-CS017       TO SXCL0170-TTR.
           MOVE VIAL0001-CALLERID        TO SXCL0170-JOBNC .
           MOVE VIAL0001-CUSER-EXTRN     TO SXCL0170-USERC .
           MOVE VIAL0001-MSGQ            TO SXCL0170-PGMQC .
           MOVE PSCK0002-RCODE-OK        TO SXCL0170-RCODE .
           MOVE PSCK0002-ESTR-EXE        TO SXCL0170-ESTR  .
           MOVE PSCK0002-APTR-APL        TO SXCL0170-APTR  .
           MOVE PSCK0002-HCLI-VMSG       TO SXCL0170-HCLI.
           MOVE PSCK0002-VNCR-NVAL       TO SXCL0170-VNCR.
           MOVE PSCK0002-PNOME-N         TO SXCL0170-PNOME.
           MOVE PSCV4010-PINCLI          TO WS-NCLI14
      *    MOVE PSCV4010-PINATRA         TO WS-NATR14
      *    MOVE PSCV4010-PINSEQA         TO WS-NSEQ14
           MOVE PSCV4010-PICONTA        TO SXCL0170-CONTA.
           MOVE PSCV4010-PINCLI          TO SXCL0170-NCLI.

           CALL SXCL0170-ROTINA USING    SXCL0002-COMMAREA,
                                         SXCL0170-DATA.
      *
           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '****-ACESSO-SXRM0170   ' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              MOVE 'SXCL0170-RCODE    '      TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-NM(1)
              MOVE SXCL0170-RCODE            TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR(1)
              MOVE 'SXCL0170-MOED     '      TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-NM(1)
              MOVE SXCL0170-MOED             TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR(1)
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.
      *
       5050-CONSULTA-CONTA-EXIT.
           EXIT.

      ******************************************************************
       5100-CALCULA-COMISSOES.
      ******************************************************************
           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '5100-CALCULA-COMISSOES.' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           INITIALIZE PSCL5035-DATA.
           MOVE WS-PROGNAME                TO PSCL5035-PGMC.
           MOVE PSCK0002-TTR-VAZIO         TO PSCL5035-TTR.
           MOVE VIAL0001-CALLERID          TO PSCL5035-JOBNC.
           MOVE VIAL0001-CUSER-EXTRN       TO PSCL5035-USERC.
           MOVE VIAL0001-MSGQ              TO PSCL5035-PGMQC.
           MOVE PSCK0002-ESTR-NEXE         TO PSCL5035-ESTR.
           MOVE PSCK0002-APTR-APL          TO PSCL5035-APTR.
           MOVE PSCV4010-PINCLI            TO PSCL5035-NCLI.
           MOVE PSCV4010-PIDINT            TO AQCW0005-DTX10.
           PERFORM AQCP0005-CONV-DT10INDT8
              THRU AQCP0005-CONV-DT10INDT8-EXIT.
           MOVE AQCW0005-DT98              TO PSCL5035-DINT.
           MOVE PSFICHREL-FRNFIC           TO PSCL5035-NFIC.
           MOVE SXCL0170-MOED              TO PSCL5035-MOED.
           MOVE PSCK0002-CANAL-AGENCIA     TO PSCL5035-CANAL.
           MOVE ZEROES                     TO PSCL5035-RCODE.
           MOVE VIAL0001-CBANCO            TO PSCL5035-AT-CBAN
           MOVE VIAL0001-CBALM             TO PSCL5035-AT-BALM
           MOVE VIAL0001-DATA-EXTRN        TO PSCL5035-AT-DTOP
           MOVE VIAL0001-CMOEDA            TO PSCL5035-AT-CMOE
           MOVE VIAL0001-I-DEBUG           TO PSCL5035-AT-DEBUG
           EVALUATE PSCV4010-PIIPAGSAL
             WHEN PSCK0002-TREMUN-SALARIO
             WHEN PSCK0002-TREMUN-BONUS
               MOVE PSCK0002-TOPE-SALARIO    TO PSCL5035-TSERV
             WHEN PSCK0002-TREMUN-FORNEC
               MOVE PSCK0002-TOPE-FORNEC     TO PSCL5035-TSERV
           END-EVALUATE

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '5100-CALCULA-COMISSOES.' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              MOVE 'PSCL5035-CANAL'          TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-NM(1)
              MOVE PSCL5035-CANAL            TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR(1)
              MOVE 'PSCL5035-MOED '          TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-NM(2)
              MOVE PSCL5035-MOED             TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR(2)
              MOVE 'PSCL5035-DINT '          TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-NM(3)
              MOVE PSCL5035-DINT             TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR(3)
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.


      *    CALL PSCK0002-PSM5035
      *         USING PSCL5035-DATA.

           PERFORM PSCP5035-CALL-PSM5035
              THRU PSCP5035-CALL-PSM5035-EXIT.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE 'FIM EXECUÇĂO PSM5035   ' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           MOVE PSCL5035-RCODE             TO VIAW0020-RCODE.

           PERFORM VIAP0020-TRATA-RCODE
              THRU VIAP0020-TRATA-RCODE-EXIT.

           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
              MOVE PSCL5035-SEQMV          TO WS-DIM-SEQMV
              MOVE PSCL5035-PACNT          TO WS-DIM-PACNT
              MOVE PSCL5035-COPER          TO WS-DIM-COPER
              MOVE PSCL5035-BALC           TO WS-DIM-BALC
              MOVE PSCL5035-CCB            TO WS-DIM-CCB
              MOVE PSCL5035-QOPER          TO WS-DIM-QOPER
              MOVE PSCL5035-VALOR          TO WS-DIM-VALOR
              MOVE PSCL5035-DESCR          TO WS-DIM-DESCR

              PERFORM 5160-CORRIGE-COMISSOES
                 THRU 5160-CORRIGE-COMISSOES-EXIT
              VARYING WS-INDICE FROM 1 BY 1
                UNTIL WS-INDICE > 100
           ELSE
              MOVE PSCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO  TO PSCV4011-PINCLI-S
              MOVE PSCK0001-ERR-CALL       TO PSCV4011-PINCLI-MSG
           END-IF.

       5100-CALCULA-COMISSOES-EXIT.
           EXIT.

      ******************************************************************
       5160-CORRIGE-COMISSOES.
      ******************************************************************
      *
           EVALUATE WS-SEQMV (WS-INDICE)
           WHEN PSCK0002-FORM-INV-MIN  THRU PSCK0002-FORM-INV-MAX
                IF PSCL5250-IIFORMT-NAO
                   MOVE 1                TO WS-QOPER (WS-INDICE)
                ELSE
                   MOVE 0                TO WS-QOPER (WS-INDICE)
                END-IF
           WHEN OTHER
                MOVE ZERO                TO WS-QOPER (WS-INDICE)
           END-EVALUATE.

      * Calculo do total de despesas efectas ao ficheiro
      * (exclu? movimenta??o contabil?stica das contrapartidas)
           IF WS-PACNT (WS-INDICE) NOT = CON-PACNT-MOV-CNT-CCB
              COMPUTE WS-TOTAL-COMISSOES = WS-TOTAL-COMISSOES +
                                         ( WS-VALOR (WS-INDICE) *
                                           WS-QOPER (WS-INDICE) )
           END-IF.

       5160-CORRIGE-COMISSOES-EXIT.
           EXIT.

      ******************************************************************
       5500-COBRANCA-DESPESAS.
      ******************************************************************
           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '5500-COBRANCA-DESPESAS.' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
              PERFORM 5550-PROC-DESPESAS
                 THRU 5550-PROC-DESPESAS-EXIT
                      VARYING WS-INDICE FROM 1 BY 1
                        UNTIL WS-INDICE > 100
           END-IF.

           MOVE ZEROES                      TO WS-COD-OPER.
           MOVE SPACES                      TO WS-DESCRICAO.
           MOVE SPACES                      TO WS-CNTA-CCB.
      *
       5500-COBRANCA-DESPESAS-EXIT.
           EXIT.

      ******************************************************************
       5550-PROC-DESPESAS.
      ******************************************************************
           MOVE WS-COPER (WS-INDICE)        TO WS-COD-OPER.
           MOVE WS-DESCR (WS-INDICE)        TO WS-DESCRICAO.
           MOVE WS-CCB   (WS-INDICE)        TO WS-CNTA-CCB.
           MOVE CON-S                       TO WS-IDSP.

           COMPUTE WS-MONTANTE  = WS-VALOR (WS-INDICE) *
                                  WS-QOPER (WS-INDICE).

           IF WS-MONTANTE > ZEROES
              PERFORM 5400-DEBITO-ORDENANTE
                 THRU 5400-DEBITO-ORDENANTE-EXIT
           END-IF.

       5550-PROC-DESPESAS-EXIT.
           EXIT.

      ******************************************************************
       5400-DEBITO-ORDENANTE.
      ******************************************************************
           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '5400-DEBITO-ORDENANTE' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF

           INITIALIZE                          PSCL5070-DATA.
           MOVE WS-PROGNAME                 TO PSCL5070-PGMC.
           MOVE PSCK0002-TTR-DEBCB          TO PSCL5070-TTR
           MOVE ZEROES                      TO PSCL5070-AUTR

           MOVE VIAL0001-CALLERID           TO PSCL5070-JOBNC.
           MOVE VIAL0001-CUSER-EXTRN        TO PSCL5070-USERC.
           MOVE VIAL0001-CUSER-EXTRN        TO PSCL5070-USER .
           MOVE VIAL0001-MSGQ               TO PSCL5070-PGMQC.
           MOVE PSCK0002-ESTR-NEXE          TO PSCL5070-ESTR.
           MOVE PSCK0002-APTR-APL           TO PSCL5070-APTR.
           MOVE PSCK0002-HCLI-BMSG          TO PSCL5070-HCLI.
           MOVE PSCV4010-PINCLI             TO PSCL5070-NCLI.
      *    MOVE PSCV4010-PINATRA            TO PSCL5070-NATR.
      *    MOVE PSCV4010-PINSEQA            TO PSCL5070-NSEQ.
           MOVE PSCV4010-PICONTA           TO PSCL5070-CONTA.
           MOVE WS-MONTANTE                 TO PSCL5070-MONT.
           MOVE WS-HEADER-NOCB              TO PSCL5070-NOPR.
           MOVE SXCL0170-MOED               TO PSCL5070-MOED.
           MOVE WS-NCLI                     TO PSCL5070-CCLI.
      ****************************************************************
           MOVE WS-IDSP                     TO PSCL5070-IDSP.
           MOVE WS-COD-OPER                 TO PSCL5070-COPE.
           MOVE WS-DESCRICAO                TO PSCL5070-DESC.
           MOVE WS-CNTA-CCB                 TO PSCL5070-CCB.
      ****************************************************************
           MOVE ZEROES                     TO PSCL5070-RCODE.
           MOVE VIAL0001-CBANCO            TO PSCL5070-AT-CBAN
           MOVE VIAL0001-CBALM             TO PSCL5070-AT-BALM
           MOVE VIAL0001-DATA-EXTRN        TO PSCL5070-AT-DTOP
           MOVE VIAL0001-CMOEDA            TO PSCL5070-AT-CMOE
           MOVE VIAL0001-I-DEBUG           TO PSCL5070-AT-DEBUG
           MOVE SXCL0170-BAL               TO PSCL5070-BALM
           MOVE PSCV4010-PIIPAGSAL         TO PSCL5070-TREMUN
           EVALUATE PSCV4010-PIIPAGSAL
             WHEN PSCK0002-TREMUN-SALARIO
             WHEN PSCK0002-TREMUN-BONUS
               MOVE PSCK0002-TOPE-SALARIO  TO PSCL5070-TOPE
             WHEN PSCK0002-TREMUN-FORNEC
               MOVE PSCK0002-TOPE-FORNEC   TO PSCL5070-TOPE
           END-EVALUATE

           IF PSCL5070-MONT IS GREATER THAN ZEROES
      *       CALL PSCK0002-PSM5070
      *            USING PSCL5070-DATA
              PERFORM PSCP5070-CALL-PSM5070
                 THRU PSCP5070-CALL-PSM5070-EXIT

              MOVE PSCL5070-RCODE          TO VIAW0020-RCODE

              PERFORM VIAP0020-TRATA-RCODE
                 THRU VIAP0020-TRATA-RCODE-EXIT

              IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
                 MOVE PSCL5070-NOPR        TO WS-HEADER-NOCB
              ELSE
                MOVE PSCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO
                                           TO PSCV4011-PINCLI-S
                MOVE PSCK0001-ERR-CALL     TO PSCV4011-PINCLI-MSG
              END-IF
           END-IF.

       5400-DEBITO-ORDENANTE-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      *==============================================================
       4000-OBTEM-CONTA.
      *****************************************************************
      *
           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '4000-OBTEM-CONTA' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              MOVE 'PSCWPS2-ORD-NIB      ' TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-NM (1)
              MOVE  PSCWPS2-ORD-NIB        TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR(1)
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF

           INITIALIZE ETCL0188-DATA   REPLACING NUMERIC BY ZEROES
                                           ALPHANUMERIC BY SPACES
      *

           MOVE PSCWPS2-ORD-NIB           TO ETCL0188-CDNIB
           SET  ETCL0188-CDTTR-CSCNT      TO TRUE

           PERFORM ETCP0002-FORM-ONLINE-IN
              THRU ETCP0002-FORM-ONLINE-IN-EXIT

           PERFORM CALL-ETR00188
              THRU CALL-ETR00188-EXIT
      *
      *
      * Se o NIB năo existir no BANKA, segue o percurso normal
      * do programa e formata o erro de cliente inexistente mais
      * ŕ frente, formata os dados da conta com a conta de input
      *

           IF NOT ETCL0002-RCODE-OK
              SET ETCL0002-RCODE-OK        TO TRUE
              MOVE ETCL0188-CDNIB-NCLI     TO PSCV4011-PINCLI-B
              MOVE ETCL0188-CDNIB-CONTA    TO PSCV4011-PICONTA-B
      * Se estiver tudo bem, usa os dados da conta devolvidos
      * pela API
           ELSE
              MOVE ETCL0188-CDNCLI         TO PSCV4011-PINCLI-B
              MOVE ETCL0188-CDCONTA        TO PSCV4011-PICONTA-B
           END-IF.
      *
           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '4000-OBTEM-CONTA-EXIT' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              MOVE 'PSCV4011-PINCLI-B  '   TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-NM(1)
              MOVE PSCV4011-PINCLI-B       TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR(1)
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.
      *
       4000-OBTEM-CONTA-EXIT.
           EXIT.

      *--------------------------------------------------------------
           EXEC SQL INCLUDE VIAP0003 END-EXEC.
           COPY ARCR5005.
           COPY AQCP0005.
           COPY AQCP0009.
           COPY VIAP0016.
           COPY VIAP0010.
           COPY VIAP0020.
           COPY PSCP5040.
           COPY PSCP5035.
           COPY PSCP5070.
           COPY ETCP0002.
           COPY ETCP0188.
           COPY AQCP0101.
